  "texts": [
    "These ranked data are then used to train a reward model, a tool for assessing AI performance.",
    "The reward model scores each response or behavior of the AI, with the scores directly reflecting the quality of its performance.",
    "Through this gradual training process, AI models can learn to handle complex tasks.",
    "Just as elementary school students improve through teacher feedback on assignments, AI uses the reward model to score its performance, identifying which behaviors are good and which need improvement to drive self-optimization.",
    "This process closely mirrors how students enhance their learning through assignment evaluation and reflection."
  ],
